summary: A preset of my high-elf female character
descriptionHtml:
Hi everybody,

Inspired from the fantastic work of [url=http://metalhed13.deviantart.com/]metalhed13[/url].

[u][b]How to install it ?[/b][/u]

Data ==> SKSE ==> Plugins ==> CharGen ==> Presets

Use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D29624&pUp=1]RaceMenu v3[/url]. During character creation (or using "showracemenu" command with the console) go to "Presets", press F9, select my preset and it's done !

[u][b]What I use :[/b][/u]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSkyHair[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty
[/url][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?]CBBE[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG Female Textures Renewal[/url]
